Version Alpha 0.2:

-> Nodes can now request local time from Border Router
-> ADDED detection mechanisms for lost connections
-> ADDED temperature and humidity functionality to Border Router and Node
-> Server can now request temperature and humidity information from all nodes at a given interval 
-> FIXED repeated MQTT message being sent by Border Router
-> Border Router can now handle more than one node (threading was not yet implemented)

Known BUGS:

-> Time information is sometimes wrong in the node





